= Rails Plugin: has_file v0.1 =
  
|| Website:   || http://code.google.com/p/rails-has-file                  ||
|| Author:    || John Wulff <johnw@orcasnet.com>                          ||
|| Copyright: || Copyright (c) 2007 John Wulff <johnw@orcasnet.com>       ||
